service green hosting by working with integrated ecosystem market services in  hostgator prepared for competition companies touting themselves as providing unlimited hosting services founder brent oxley was adamant about being able to back up an unlimited option prior to offering service named as such and increased staffing he suggested that this move increased sales by at least  in  an office was added in austin texas in  hostgator started operations in india with a its office in nashik maharashtra and a data centre on  june  ceo and founder brent oxley announced the sale of hostgator to endurance international group advised employees and users not to worry in part because oxley would still own the buildings hostgator used he said he wanted to travel the world before he had children he was also candid about the failures in creating stable billing and register portions of hostgator and hoped that endurance might fix those hostgator was sold to endurance international group for  million  as of  hostgator hosts over  million domains and has over  customers incidentsedit  social engineering attackedit further information ugnazi § whmcsleak in may  the computer hacker group ugnazi claimed responsibility for hacking the web server of the web host billing software developer whmcs in an apparent social engineering attack involving hostgator a member of the group cosmo called whmcss hosting provider impersonating a senior employee they were subsequently granted root access to whmcss web server after providing information for identity verification ugnazi later leaked publicly whmcss sql database containing user information and  customer credit cards website files and cpanel configuration after this issue whmcs emailed members to change their passwords  service outagesedit since its acquisition by endurance international hostgator has suffered an increased incidence of server outages and downtime notably on august   and december   endurance international group’s data center in provo utah experienced network outages that affected thousands of customers of bluehost hostgator hostmonster and justhost spring  blackoutsedit during the afternoon of april   the data center in provo utah experienced a networking issue that affected customers of hostgator hostmonster  bluehost the issue was fully rectified only after  hours on april    am there was another outage on may   that took nearly  hours to completely resolve this problem occurred in the same data center october  outageedit during the morning of october   hostgator suffered another major outage that affected their reseller accounts the company did not immediately announce the cause of the outage though they stated on facebook and their forum that an os upgrade was the cause of the issue they made the reseller sections of their forum inaccessible to the public visible only to registered users the serverlevel problems were resolved on november   almost five days after the outage began on november   users were still reporting widespread accountlevel database problems december  outageedit during the afternoon and evening of december   hostgator experienced a major outage in their twitter account they said we are seeing problems w network flapping which could be caused by denial of service or other network issues in our switching fabric we are methodically isolating the issue while making sure we dont deteriorate the network further its a large network and we are working on it in sections our best team is working through this at our data center and it is our goal to have this resolved very soon in other words we know this is frustrating and we are on it again our sincere apologies for this inconvenience referencesedit  hostgatorcom whois dns  domain info  domaintools whois retrieved    hostgator  business services inc profile inc magazine  retrieved    about us  hostgator wwwhostgatorcom retrieved    harrell barry may   hostgator expanding to austin bringing  jobs austinamerican statesman ret